{"tid":284744,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"「２０１７十大最佳旅行城市」","createTime":"2017-06-15T07:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T02:00:25.000Z","uid":89368,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"710d44ba85fcffdc93072e42af3196f37de04944","tid":284744,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我「玩野」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n知名旅遊指南出版社《孤獨星球》（Lonely Planet）票選2017年最佳旅行地推薦&mdash;Best in Travel 2017，為全球旅行者提供2017年最值得去的目的地指南。<br />\n<br />\n分爲<br />\n「2017年全球十大最佳旅遊國家」、<br />\n「最佳旅遊城市」、<br />\n「最佳旅遊區域」三個類別<br />\n<br />\n今次就講<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「最佳旅遊城市」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n十大最佳旅行城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/153211_b258068e7655ebe437de4f3bdf93e029.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F153211_b258068e7655ebe437de4f3bdf93e029.jpg&h=64100088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1.波爾多（Bordeaux），法國</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/153008_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F153008_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=a881e8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國最著名的葡萄酒產區。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">2.開普敦（Cape Town），南非</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152958_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152958_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=bb19e2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開普敦正變得越來越全球化，是新興的美食城市。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">3.洛杉磯，美國</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152946_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152946_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=4dd21084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豐富的美食、美麗的海灘、博物館和劇院比任何其它美國城市多。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">4.梅里達（M&eacute;rida），墨西哥</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152935_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152935_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=d7936073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該市有很多現場音樂、藝術節，以及瑪雅遺蹟和文物。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">5.奧赫里德（Ohrid），馬其頓（Macedonia）</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152919_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152919_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=6ac3386a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n該市有古老的城堡和教堂，戶外活動包括租船活動、沙灘運動，或在周圍的森林徒步旅行、騎自行車。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">6.皮斯托亞（Pistoia），意大利</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152909_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152909_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=dad8384d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皮斯托亞被稱為「小佛羅倫薩」，在2017年成為意大利文化之都。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">7.首爾，韓國</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152853_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152853_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=9b425620&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首爾是韓國商業和文化的完美結合。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">8.里斯本，葡萄牙</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152837_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152837_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg&h=91af006b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐洲實惠的旅遊地點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">9.莫斯科，俄羅斯</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152813_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152813_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg&h=1a5e9938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將承辦2018年世界盃足球賽。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">10.波特蘭，美國俄勒岡</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/15/152741_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F15%2F152741_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg&h=e547b5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這是一座友好和可持續發展的城市，十分重視生活質量。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考自<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/10/26/n8433676.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F10%2F26%2Fn8433676.htm&d=lxsB7AtX3krfHzn%2BLtkFW57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1f1e9ac7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/10/26/n8433676.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">如果大家都鍾支睇希望LIKE一LIKE以下呢個PAGE啦，岩岩新開的，希望大家支持</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%A9%E9%87%8E-1842596556058904/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E7%258E%25A9%25E9%2587%258E-1842596556058904%2F&d=lxsB7AtX3krfHzn%2BLtkFW57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=1cf9f4a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E7%8E%A9%E9%87%8E-1842596556058904/</a><br />\n<br />\n我都會俾心機出多Ｄ有趣話題等大家睇睇，希望大家睇得開心。<br />\n歡迎大家俾更多意見，多謝"},{"pid":"7b8062cdab31c60b3579c7eb7487bb81ba688534","tid":284744