gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29c0c53c8cf29a649b9a81d4936fea89ca70b48","tid":284744,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"樓主好強，今年去過全世界？"},{"pid":"c623df793331156e28d1f44e0e6661b455766c38","tid":284744,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:53:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好強，今年去過全世界？</blockquote><br />\n遊指南出版社《孤獨星球》（Lonely Planet）票選咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1個都未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e5fe186857bdb42d96ae31001f77c31c24583b","tid":284744,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"出多D有趣話題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想人睇你個PAGE至少都加D自己意見呀資料下落去啦, 你而家只係就咁轉貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4196a987bf404ff7fb74041714e1ce0104d2b4","tid":284744,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"冇倫敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62aaf095a7535d81b9a2b06bf663921ae9aa3d8","tid":284744,"uid":51033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T08:57:57.000Z","msg":"以上地區準備比蝗蹂躪"},{"pid":"f74862727c27e5395d0707245d26b8e46454c1d6","tid":284744,"uid":89368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出多D有趣話題? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想人睇你個PAGE至少都加D自己意見呀資料下落去啦, 你而家只係就咁轉貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal